These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
House: cottage, futuristic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| House     | futuristic | cottage  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, roller
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Transport   | roller | ship   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different pets are kept: bird, cat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Pet   | bird  | cat |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

